@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get price (cached path)
GET {{baseUrl}}/price/1

### Get price directly from DB (no cache)
GET {{baseUrl}}/price-db/1

### Missing product (expects 404 ProblemDetail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/price/999999999

### Replace adjustments for a product
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/price/1/adjustments
Content-Type: application/json

[
  { "type": "ABSOLUTE", "mode": "ADD", "amount": 1.25 },
  { "type": "PERCENT", "mode": "ADD", "amount": 10 }
]

### Seed dataset (override defaults)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/seed?count=100000&adjustRate=0.1&clear=true

### Clear all data
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/clear
